text: Henry Noga was a U.S. soccer goalkeeper who earned two caps with the U.S. national team. Both games, which were World Cup qualifiers, came in November 1960. The first was a 3-3 tie with Mexico on November 6. The second was a 3-0 loss to Mexico seven days later.USA - Details of International Matches 1885-1969 ==References== ==External links== * Category:United States men's international soccer players Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:American soccer players Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
